Enum Class RoomPreference

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<RoomPreference>
structures.RoomPreference
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<RoomPreference>, Constable
public enum RoomPreference extends Enum<RoomPreference>
The RoomPreference class hosts a series of constant values referring to ISCTE-IUL room specifications. They are used to represent a user's room specification preferences when rescheduling a class, or scheduling an entire new course.
Since:
1.0
